  "text": "In the full theory, we tensor together these operators with the flat space operators as in (2.3). The physical operators are obtained by imposing BRST invariance and a GSO projection which tie together the two Hilbert spaces. [CITATION_1] The negative sign follows from the axial gauging of the coset.",
